---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

// Live demo — WordPress Playground.
// Blueprint at /public/playground/theme-blueprint.json:
//   1. Installs WP + WC
//   2. Fetches asteris-theme.zip from this same domain (must be public)
//   3. Activates the theme
//   4. Imports WordPress theme unit test content so the front end has real posts/pages
//
// Boot ~30-60s first time. Subsequent visits cached by Playground.
const PLAYGROUND_URL = 'https://playground.wordpress.net/?blueprint-url=https://asteriscommerce.com/playground/theme-blueprint.json';
---
<Layout
  title="Try the Asteris theme — live in your browser, no install"
  description="A WordPress + WooCommerce + Asteris Theme sandbox running entirely in your browser via WordPress Playground. Click through the 14 product page templates, 4 style variations, and 18 per-product fields without installing anything."
>
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="eyebrow">★ LIVE IN YOUR BROWSER</div>
      <h1>Try the Asteris theme.<br /><span class="accent">No install. No signup.</span></h1>
      <p class="lead">
        A real WordPress install with <strong>WooCommerce + the Asteris theme</strong> active, running entirely in your browser via <strong>WordPress Playground</strong>. Browse the front end, open the Site Editor, switch between the 4 style variations, click into any of the 14 product page templates.
      </p>
      <p class="boot">First boot takes ~30–60 seconds while Playground spins up WordPress + WooCommerce + the Asteris theme. Subsequent boots are cached.</p>
      <div class="hactions">
        <a href={PLAYGROUND_URL} target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn-pop btn-large">★ Launch the demo →</a>
        <a href="/asteris-theme/" class="btn-outline btn-large">Or read about the theme</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="status">
    <div class="container narrow">
      <div class="sbox">
        <div class="seye">★ LIVE DEMO — FREE, GPL, NOTHING TO BUY</div>
        <p>The Playground blueprint installs WordPress, WooCommerce, and the Asteris theme, then imports sample posts so the front end isn't empty. First boot takes 30–60 seconds. Want it on your own site instead? <a href="/asteris-theme/#download">Download the theme ZIP</a> or install from WordPress.org once we land there.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="active">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>What to click first</h2>
      <p class="csub">The demo loads at the front end. Here's a 60-second tour worth taking:</p>
      <div class="agrid">
        <div class="acol">
          <h3>Front-end clicks</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Browse the home page — 0 KB JavaScript, full-bleed images, system fonts</li>
            <li>Hit <strong>/shop/</strong> to see the WooCommerce loop</li>
            <li>Open any product to see the default template</li>
            <li>Resize the window to check mobile behaviour</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="acol">
          <h3>Admin clicks</h3>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Appearance → Editor</strong> to open the Site Editor</li>
            <li><strong>Styles</strong> (sidebar) to switch between the 4 variations: Classic / Editorial / Minimal / Dark</li>
            <li><strong>Templates → Single Product</strong> shows all 14 product templates</li>
            <li><strong>Products → Edit any product</strong> — bound fields appear in the sidebar (BNPL, ingredients, spec table, etc.)</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="limits">
    <div class="container narrow">
      <h2>What works in Playground vs what doesn't</h2>
      <div class="lgrid">
        <div class="lcol works">
          <h3>★ Works</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Full WordPress + WooCommerce admin</li>
            <li>All 14 product page templates</li>
            <li>All 4 style variations (Classic / Editorial / Minimal / Dark)</li>
            <li>Site Editor — edit anything live</li>
            <li>The 18 per-product content fields</li>
            <li>Cart + checkout templates</li>
            <li>Importing sample posts + pages from WP theme test data</li>
            <li>Switching templates per product</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="lcol limited">
          <h3>★ Limited / unavailable</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Real payments (WC checkout works but no Stripe/PayPal in-sandbox)</li>
            <li>Outbound email (WC notification mail is logged, not sent)</li>
            <li>No persistent storage — close the tab and everything resets</li>
            <li>No Asteris paid plugins active — this demo is the theme only</li>
            <li>Pro Patterns isn't loaded here — see <a href="/try-pro-patterns/">the Pro Patterns demo</a> for that</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="after">
    <div class="container narrow">
      <h2>After the demo.</h2>
      <p>Like what you see? The theme is free under GPL-2.0+ and stays free forever. Download the ZIP and upload via Appearance → Themes → Add New → Upload.</p>
      <div class="aactions">
        <a href="/asteris-theme/#download" class="btn-pop btn-large">★ Download Asteris v1.0.0 →</a>
        <a href="/asteris-pro-patterns/" class="btn-outline btn-large">Or add Pro Patterns ($49) →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .container { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 36px; }
  .narrow { max-width: 820px; }

  .hero { padding: 80px 0 48px; }
  .hero .eyebrow {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--c-violet);
    color: #fff;
    padding: 6px 14px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .hero h1 { font-size: clamp(40px, 7vw, 80px); line-height: 0.98; letter-spacing: -2px; font-weight: 900; margin: 0 0 28px; }
  .hero h1 .accent { background: linear-gradient(transparent 55%, rgba(170, 0, 255, 0.20) 55%); padding: 0 4px; }
  .hero .lead { font-size: 20px; max-width: 760px; color: var(--c-text); line-height: 1.55; margin-bottom: 14px; }
  .hero .lead strong { color: var(--c-text); font-weight: 700; }
  .hero .boot { font-size: 15px; color: var(--c-muted); margin-bottom: 28px; }
  .hactions { display: flex; gap: 14px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .btn-large { padding: 16px 28px; font-size: 17px; font-weight: 700; border: 2px solid var(--c-black); border-radius: var(--r-md); text-decoration: none; }
  .btn-pop { background: var(--c-violet); color: #fff; border-color: var(--c-violet); }
  .btn-outline { background: transparent; color: var(--c-black); }
  .btn-pop:hover, .btn-outline:hover { transform: translate(-2px, -2px); box-shadow: var(--pop-shadow); }

  .status { padding: 32px 0; background: rgba(170, 0, 255, 0.08); }
  .sbox { background: var(--c-white); border: 2px solid var(--c-text); border-radius: 8px; padding: 22px 24px; }
  .seye { color: var(--c-violet); font-weight: 800; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .sbox p { font-size: 16px; color: var(--c-text); line-height: 1.55; margin: 0; }
  .sbox a { color: var(--c-violet); text-decoration: underline; font-weight: 600; }

  .active { padding: 80px 0; background: var(--c-white); border-top: 2px solid var(--c-text); border-bottom: 2px solid var(--c-text); }
  .active h2 { font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 42px); font-weight: 900; letter-spacing: -1.5px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .csub { font-size: 17px; color: var(--c-muted); max-width: 760px; line-height: 1.55; margin-bottom: 28px; }
  .agrid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 24px; }
  .acol h3 { font-size: 21px; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 14px; color: var(--c-violet); }
  .acol ul { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0; }
  .acol li { padding: 6px 0 6px 22px; position: relative; font-size: 16px; color: var(--c-text); line-height: 1.5; }
  .acol li::before { content: '→'; position: absolute; left: 0; color: var(--c-violet); font-weight: 700; }
  @media (max-width: 800px) { .agrid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }

  .limits { padding: 80px 0; background: var(--c-bg); }
  .limits h2 { font-size: clamp(24px, 3vw, 36px); font-weight: 900; letter-spacing: -1.2px; margin-bottom: 24px; }
  .lgrid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 18px; }
  .lcol { border: 2px solid var(--c-text); border-radius: 8px; padding: 22px; background: var(--c-white); }
  .works h3 { color: #1a7f37; font-size: 19px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .limited h3 { color: #c0392b; font-size: 19px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .lcol ul { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0; }
  .lcol li { padding: 6px 0 6px 22px; position: relative; font-size: 15px; color: var(--c-text); line-height: 1.55; }
  .works li::before { content: '✓'; position: absolute; left: 0; color: #1a7f37; font-weight: 800; }
  .limited li::before { content: '⚠'; position: absolute; left: 0; color: #c0392b; }
  .lcol a { color: var(--c-violet); text-decoration: underline; }
  @media (max-width: 800px) { .lgrid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }

  .after { padding: 80px 0; background: var(--c-text); color: var(--c-white); text-align: center; border-top: 6px solid var(--c-violet); }
  .after h2 { font-size: clamp(32px, 4vw, 42px); font-weight: 900; letter-spacing: -1.5px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: #fff; }
  .after p { font-size: 18px; color: #ccc; max-width: 680px; margin: 0 auto 24px; line-height: 1.6; }
  .aactions { display: flex; gap: 14px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .after .btn-outline { background: var(--c-white); color: var(--c-text); border-color: var(--c-white); }
</style>
